418: ## Recovery Procedures
419: 
420: ### Data Recovery
421: 
422: 1. Backup verification:
423: 
424: ```typescript
425: async function verifyBackups(): Promise<boolean> {
426:   const backups = await db.collection('backups').get();
427:   return backups.size > 0;
428: }
429: ```
